title: Lattice Light Sheet Sample Data - EB3/H2B (mitosis)
description: A raw sample dataset collected on a lattice light sheet in stage scanning mode.  Deskewing required.  Depicts anaphase with microtubule tip binding protein EB3 labeled with EGFP and histone H2B labeled with mCherry.  600 volumetric frames in 2 channels, with a 3.87 second inter-frame interval.

attributes.Description: Zip file containing the full dataset
